{
  "workflow_id": "standard_qa",
  "description": "标准检索生成与审核流程（包含动态工具路由循环）",
  "entry_point": "parser",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "name": "parser",
      "model": "deepseek-chat",
      "temperature": 0.3,
      "system_prompt": "请从以下用户输入中提取出最核心的搜索关键词，不要输出任何其他废话。",
      "api": "DEEPSEEK_API_KEY",
      "base_url": "https://api.deepseek.com",
      "output_key": "parsed_query",
      "tools": []
    },
    {
      "name": "search",
      "model": "deepseek-chat",
      "temperature": 0.3,
      "system_prompt": "你是一个搜索智能体。请观察上下文，如果需要查阅资料，请调用搜索工具；如果不需要或已经获得足够信息，请直接输出“搜索完毕”。",
      "api": "DEEPSEEK_API_KEY",
      "base_url": "https://api.deepseek.com",
      "output_key": "search_results",
      "tools": [
        "web_search"
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "generator",
      "model": "deepseek-chat",
      "temperature": 0.3,
      "system_prompt": "你是一个内容生成助手。请严格结合下方的上下文状态（特别是搜索结果），按照以下格式整理内容:\n解决方案: \n参考资料：",
      "api": "DEEPSEEK_API_KEY",
      "base_url": "https://api.deepseek.com",
      "output_key": "draft",
      "tools": []
    },
    {
      "name": "reviewer",
      "model": "deepseek-chat",
      "temperature": 0.3,
      "system_prompt": "你是一个严苛的质量审核员。请判断生成的草稿是否完美解答了用户的问题。\n请严格以 JSON 格式返回结果，包含 is_approved (布尔值) 和 feedback (修改建议) 两个字段。",
      "api": "DEEPSEEK_API_KEY",
      "base_url": "https://api.deepseek.com",
      "output_key": "feedback",
      "tools": []
    }
  ],
  "edges": [
    {
      "from": "parser",
      "to": "search"
    },
    {
      "from": "tool_executor",
      "to": "search"
    },
    {
      "from": "generator",
      "to": "reviewer"
    }
  ],
  "conditional_edges": [
    {
      "from": "search",
      "router": "check_tool_calls",
      "mapping": {
        "execute_tools": "tool_executor",
        "next_step": "generator"
      }
    },
    {
      "from": "reviewer",
      "router": "should_continue",
      "mapping": {
        "END": "END",
        "generator": "generator"
      }
    }
  ]
}